{"tid":359534,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[派膠學生的好西]午餐:14/8/17","createTime":"2017-08-14T14:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T14:36:13.000Z","uid":134220,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b838fcd53c74ada4e04f0f89a81137ae58c3c7","tid":359534,"uid":134220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"今日完全係韓餐上左theone果個空中花園食飯 70蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過100分好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/14/222248_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F14%2F222248_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=440dd455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓式炸雞+年糕 （左 60）原味紫菜包飯 （中 60）濟州三多水2公升（右 10）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/14/222751_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F14%2F222751_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a0767740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先講碗炸雞先 開頭老闆娘同我講話有少少辣所以我買咗碗細 但係食食下覺得好好味突然有少少後悔點解自己買咗碗細嘅買大嘅 <br />\n炸雞個皮係卜卜脆嘅一面係熱辣辣嘅雞肉 唔算辣 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/14/223334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F14%2F223334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c3bc5ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住講個飯卷 麻油分量啱啱好 入面啲料好充足食到飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/14/223438_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F14%2F223438_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f6724e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/14/223444_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F14%2F223444_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1cf80e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上呢兩樣嘢都係喺尖沙咀金巴利街嗰間新世界美食嗰度買 d auntie全部都係韓國人嚟嘅不過講廣東話非常之好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後嗰啲十蚊水真係好正兩公升喎 喺第二間新世界買 其實上條街全部都係新世界只不過係唔同人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}